output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: No visible CMF number, but this doesn't automatically disqualify it as propaganda.
2. Refers to candidate: Yes, explicitly mentions "George Simion" and positions him as "președintele României" - directly referring to a presidential candidate.
3. Addresses wide population: Yes - It's a paid advertisement with 20,000-24,999 impressions - Uses inclusive language ("investițiile în afacerea și locuința ta") - Uses call-to-action directed at general public ("Votați")
4. Electoral objective: Clearly yes - Direct call to vote ("Votați AUR și George Simion") - Positions candidate as "președintele României" - Uses campaign hashtags - Clear intention to influence voting behavior
5. Journalism: No - This is clearly a campaign message - No journalistic content or informative purpose - Pure advocacy and call to action
6. Personal opinion: No - This is a paid advertisement from "UNIWORLD - MEDIA SRL" - Structured as a campaign message - Professional marketing approach

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post clearly constitutes electoral propaganda because: - Explicitly promotes a presidential candidate - Makes a direct call to vote - Uses campaign messaging and hashtags - Is a paid advertisement reaching a large audience - Has clear electoral objectives
conclusion.message-for-police: UNIWORLD - MEDIA SRL, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin difuzarea unui mesaj de propaganda electorala dupa incheierea perioadei de campanie electorala, la data de 23.11.2024 dupa ora 18:00. Postarea cu ID-ul 1611606109739658 contine un indemn direct la vot pentru candidatul AUR la presedintie, George Simion, utilizand formularea explicita "Votați AUR și George Simion, președintele României!", alaturi de hashtag-uri de campanie. Mesajul are un evident caracter de propaganda electorala, fiind o reclama platita care a ajuns la 20.000-24.999 de persoane, cu un buget intre 200-299 RON, avand ca scop influentarea directa a intentiei de vot a alegatorilor pentru candidatul AUR la functia de presedinte al Romaniei.
